H0.text: The name Benedict, as used by popes, etc., is from the Latin meaning. Bless

H1.text: The name Benedict, as used by popes, etc., is from the Latin meaning. Well-Spoken

H2.text: The name Benedict, as used by popes, etc., is from the Latin meaning. Gift

H3.text: The name Benedict, as used by popes, etc., is from the Latin meaning. Beatify

A4.text: Benedict XVI chose his papal name, which comes from the Latin word meaning 'the blessed', in honour of both Benedict XV and Benedict of Nursia.
